1. As a customer, I want to receive timely updates on the status of my shipment, including tracking information, to ensure I am informed about the delivery progress.

2. As a customer, I want the option to choose from different shipping methods at checkout, allowing me to prioritize speed or cost according to my needs.

3. As a customer, I want to easily access and review the shipping costs associated with my order before completing the purchase, ensuring transparency in pricing.

4. As a customer, I want the option to provide specific delivery instructions or preferences during the checkout process, such as leaving the package at a designated location.

5. As a customer, I want to be notified promptly if there are any delays or issues with my shipment, along with clear information on how the situation is being addressed.

6. As a customer, I want the eCommerce platform to automatically calculate and display estimated delivery dates based on the chosen shipping method and my location.

7. As a customer, I want the option to easily return or exchange items in case of any shipping-related issues, with a straightforward and user-friendly return process.

8. As a customer, I want the eCommerce website to provide accurate shipping costs based on my location and the items in my cart, avoiding any surprises during the checkout process.

9. As a customer, I want the ability to track my shipment in real-time through a user-friendly interface, allowing me to anticipate the delivery time and plan accordingly.

10. As a customer, I want the eCommerce website to offer a reliable and secure shipping service, ensuring that my items arrive in good condition and as expected.